    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/bfe1b9d46cf01717ed7a16b2c3e02a70.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/00a474010eae8440610dd9d87a599c0c.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=80 /></span>在命运般的一天，高濑律遇见了来自遥远世界的魔法生物——莉莉，并与她达成了一项协议。这项协议可能让律的生活重回正轨……也可能让她陷入更深的困境。作为交换，莉莉治愈了律的腿伤，而正是这次腿伤让律失去了在名门古宫学园田径队的位置。为了复原，律同意成为莉莉的战士，化身为魔法少女，与邪恶势力对抗！加入她们，面对神秘怪物和那些试图释放怪物的人，一同展开激烈战斗吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在此过程中，她们还必须应对一个腐败的学生会。这个学生会利用自己的权力来满足他们最黑暗的欲望。而在暗地里中，一家可疑的制药公司帝国也在操控着古宫学园以及新町这个小镇的方方面面！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/9c868e4b7cfd7a6505cd42375fcbc215.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/1fb08e743550528f71959604c77fddf3.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/e0cfe97abe2b07ca64530b21fd035878.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/1856dd63bdcbb14a98e34146d397831e.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/6ef1e2cf0547191bbbbdd8fb21b21e06.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/00a474010eae8440610dd9d87a599c0c.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在经典的回合制战斗系统中与敌人交锋。敌人会试图束缚、毒害或眩晕律，企图用邪恶的手抓住她，所以你必须保持警惕，制定不同的策略来应对所有敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070610/extras/2d514c0cbc0c8b0fcd3b294900be6d23.avif?t=1762571068\" width=617 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技能树</strong>：丰富的技能选择让你可以根据自己的喜好定制律的战斗风格。你会将莉莉培养成一个用拳头伸张正义的物理战士，还是让她掌握新获得的魔法力量，消灭敌人？选择权在你手中！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>场景探索</strong>：探索广阔的世界，发现事件和资源，用于制作物品并提升律的技能和力量，以更好地面对她的敌人！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
